d about 18 percent. Panama's ad ranking system, which surfaces sponsored search results based on click rate in addition to how much advertisers pay, is an improvement from Yahoo's prior system, which surfaced ads based solely on price paid in auction. Panama also allows advertisers to target ads geographically. Panama's biggest success to date was a deal with Viacom to provide sponsored search and contextual ads to 33 of its entertainment sites. Viacom is suing Google for $1 billion over copy-right infringement on Google Video and YouTube. for the latest news, views and analysis on enterprise search technology. RSS feed to your feed reader so that you don't miss another headline! Fill-in form below to apply. ZIFF DAVIS MEDIA ESEMINARS AT Jun 5, 12 p.m. ET Power Up! Power Architecture Enhancement Details Sponsored by Mainline Information Services Jun 5, 12:30 p.m. ET Knowing and Controlling TCO Sponsored by PC Connection & HP Jun 5, 2 p.m. ET Solving the Challenges of Remote PC Administration for State & Local Government Jun 7, 12 p.m. ET Data Loss Prevention: Vital Tools and Critical Tasks Datacenters: Scaling Your Enterprise with Blade Servers Sponsored by Dell & Cisco Top Considerations for Managing Virtual Platform Environments Backup Exec 11d - The Gold Standard in Windows Data Recovery VARcast: Grow Your Windows Revenue with Backup Exec System Recovery Learn about Extended Validation from VeriSign Microsoft&reg; evaluation software & exclusive tools! Secure File Transfer: FREE trial of WS_FTP Server! Control PDF files with Adobe&reg; Acrobat&reg; 8. Learn more Tame data with the HP StorageWorks All-in-One Storage System. Access the SOA Resource Center for a wide range of SOA-related analyst reports, white papers, standards and best practices. Keep your productivity up! Make your network fast, reliable and secure with Radware eFax Corporate: #1 fax-server alternative &#150; TRIAL OFFER. Bring together global collaborators from any location at any time. Nortel is